Introduction
=============

hwdb-opendpi is a project that tries to integrate opendpi library in the hwdb streaming 
database infrustructure. 

Build
=====

cd opendpi/
./autgen.sh
./configure
make
cd ../libhashish
make

Usage
=====

./hwdb_opendpi [-i dev_name] [-r pcap_file]


Upgradding opendpi code
=======================

cd opendpi
git svn rebase
git push

